item.title: Figuring it out again
item.description: from me Been a while since I made a blog post having pulled back for a variety of reasons. Even as I was creating this entry it occurred to me again how draining and contrived it felt to concept these things and practice restraint, make sure I’m projecting as “acceptable” image, create and upload free models to link and keep the analytics active. But it also wasn’t the case of taking a social media break to reset.
